// =============================================================================
// net/quic/stream_sm/mod.vr — QUIC stream state machines + flow control
// =============================================================================
// Layer: 5 (Network — QUIC)
// Spec: internal/specs/tls-quic.md §7, §12 Phase 4
// =============================================================================
//
// Per-direction stream state machines + the connection-level flow-
// control accountant. Module named `stream_sm` (not `stream`) to
// avoid colliding with the existing intrinsic-backed
// `core.net.quic.stream` wrapper during the co-existence phase.
//
// # Module layout
//
// ```
// core.net.quic.stream_sm
// ├── mod.vr            ← this file (re-exports)
// ├── send.vr           — RFC 9000 §3.1 sender state machine
// ├── recv.vr           — RFC 9000 §3.2 receiver state machine
// └── flow_control.vr   — RFC 9000 §4 connection FC + stream-count FC
// ```
//
// =============================================================================

module core.net.quic.stream_sm;

public module send;
public module recv;
public module flow_control;

// Re-exports
public mount .send.{SendStream, SendState, SendError};
public mount .recv.{RecvStream, RecvState, RecvError};
public mount .flow_control.{ConnFlowControl};
